  },
  {
    year: 2020,
    title: 'Digital Transformation & Research Portal Launch',
    description: 'Launched proprietary research portal delivering real-time intelligence, commodity pricing data, and historical analysis archives. Digital delivery transformed client workflows. Subscription model scaled to 120+ institutional clients across 30 countries.',
  },
  {
    year: 2025,
    title: 'Current Standing: Global Research Leadership',
    description: '18 years of independent market intelligence. 47 active market coverage. 320+ published reports. 120+ institutional clients. 320+ analyst interviews annually. Ranked #1 independent research provider by institutional buy-side survey.',
  },
